OL,3,CNational Memorial Arboretum unveils
OL,4,Crestoration of memorial
OL,6,FThe National Memorial Arboretum is
OL,7,Funveiling a restoration of one of its
OL,8,Fmemorials this weekend.
OL,10,F'Shot at Dawn' commemorates 309
OL,11,FBritish and Commonwealth soldiers who
OL,12,Fwere shot for desertion, cowardice,
OL,13,Fstriking a senior officer, disobeying
OL,14,Fa lawful order, casting away arms,
OL,15,Fmutiny and sleeping at post during the
OL,16,FFirst World War.
OL,18,FMost of the soldiers who were shot
OL,19,Fwere sentenced after a short trial and
OL,20,Fweren't given fair opportunity to
OL,21,Fdefence.
